event.title: FOSS Meetup Lucknow
event.metaDesc: Join the FOSS United community in Lucknow for a meetup focused on open source software.
event.content: Join the FOSS United community in Lucknow for a meetup focused on open source software. This in-person gathering provides an opportunity to connect with fellow open source enthusiasts, developers, and maintainers in the Lucknow area.
